206 /* Define or comment out the cipher suites you'd like to be compiled in
207  make sure to use at least one BUILD_SSL_xxx or BUILD_TLS_xxx is defined
208 
209  When adding cipher suites, add name to cipher_names, idx to cipher_name_idx
210 
211  Now that there is a maximum strength crypto build, the following BUILD_XXX
212  flags need to be divided into two groups selected by WOLFSSL_MAX_STRENGTH.
213  Those that do not use Perfect Forward Security and do not use AEAD ciphers
214  need to be switched off. Allowed suites use (EC)DHE, AES-GCM|CCM, or
215  CHACHA-POLY.
216 */
217 
218 /* Check that if WOLFSSL_MAX_STRENGTH is set that all the required options are
219  * not turned off. */
220 #if defined(WOLFSSL_MAX_STRENGTH) && \
221  ((!defined(HAVE_ECC) && (defined(NO_DH) || defined(NO_RSA))) || \
222  (!defined(HAVE_AESGCM) && !defined(HAVE_AESCCM) && \
223  (!defined(HAVE_POLY1305) || !defined(HAVE_CHACHA))) || \
224  (defined(NO_SHA256) && !defined(WOLFSSL_SHA384)) || \
225  !defined(NO_OLD_TLS))
226 
227  #error "You are trying to build max strength with requirements disabled."
228 #endif
